<div id="banner">
	<h1>Tufte</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>Today I took a one-day course from <a href="http://www.edwardtufte.com/">Edward Tufte</a>, the infodesign maven. He was surprisingly kind and silly &#8212; not what I expected from his writing. He was both entertaining and informative and I had a great time. I took a lot of notes, hopefully I can write them up soon.</p>

<p class="posted">posted September 26, 2002 09:57 PM (<a class="category" href="cat_superheroes">Superheroes</a>)  <a href="000617" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
